---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { buttonVariants } from "../components/ui/button";
import Slide from "../components/Slide.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Return Policy - Thetis Medical"
    description="Our 30-day return policy for Thetis Medical products. Learn about returns, refunds, and our customer service process."
>
    <main class="">
        <Slide title="Return Policy">
            <div class="space-y-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
                <div class="bg-white shadow-lg p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <h2 class="mb-6 font-semibold text-2xl">
                        30-Day Return Policy
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
                        We have a 30-day return policy, which means you have 30
                        days after receiving your item to request a return.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-xl">
                        Return Requirements
                    </h3>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
                        To be eligible for a return, your item must be in the
                        same condition that you received it, unworn or unused,
                        with tags, and in its original packaging.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-xl">
                        How to Start a Return
                    </h3>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <p class="text-gray-700">You can start a return by:</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
                            <li>
                                Contacting us at <a
                                    href="mailto:info@thetismedical.com"
                                    class="text-primary hover:underline"
                                    >info@thetismedical.com</a
                                > with your order ID, reason for return, and photos
                                if required
                            </li>
                            <li>Using our online returns form below</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-blue-50 mt-8 p-6 rounded-lg">
                        <h4 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-lg">
                            Quick Return Process
                        </h4>
                        <ol class="space-y-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-decimal">
                            <li>
                                Submit your return request with order details
                            </li>
                            <li>We'll review and approve your return</li>
                            <li>We'll send you a return shipping label</li>
                            <li>Ship your item back to us</li>
                            <li>
                                We'll process your refund within 10 business
                                days
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white shadow-lg p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <h2 class="mb-6 font-semibold text-2xl">
                        Damages and Issues
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
                        Please inspect your order upon reception and contact us
                        immediately if the item is defective, damaged, or if you
                        receive the wrong item, so that we can evaluate the
                        issue and make it right.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white shadow-lg p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <h2 class="mb-6 font-semibold text-2xl">
                        Non-Returnable Items & Conditions
                    </h2>

                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <h3 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-red-600 text-xl">
                            ðŸš« Sorry, We Can't Accept These Returns
                        </h3>
                        <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
                            We know it's not fun to hear "no," but these
                            conditions make it impossible for us to resell the
                            product or are outside our control:
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="pl-4 border-red-500 border-l-4">
                            <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-lg">
                                Doctor Didn't Approve? ðŸ˜…
                            </h4>
                            <p class="mb-2 text-gray-700">
                                We always recommend checking with your
                                healthcare provider before purchasing.
                                Unfortunately, if your doctor says "no thanks,"
                                we can't accept that as a return reason. Your
                                doctor knows best!
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="pl-4 border-red-500 border-l-4">
                            <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-lg">
                                Product Made Unsellable
                            </h4>
                            <p class="mb-2 text-gray-700">
                                We need to be able to resell returned items to
                                keep our prices low. These conditions make that
                                impossible:
                            </p>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
                                <li>
                                    <strong>Stretched or curling straps:</strong
                                    > Once stretched, they won't provide the proper
                                    support
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <strong
                                        >Skin on straps or foam backing:</strong
                                    > We love you, but we don't want your skin cells!
                                    ðŸ˜„
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <strong>Damaged packaging:</strong> We need ALL
                                    parts back in good condition - it's like a puzzle,
                                    every piece matters!
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="pl-4 border-red-500 border-l-4">
                            <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-lg">
                                Other Non-Returnable Items
                            </h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
                                <li>
                                    Perishable goods (food, flowers, plants)
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Custom products (special orders or
                                    personalized items)
                                </li>
                                <li>Personal care goods (beauty products)</li>
                                <li>
                                    Hazardous materials, flammable liquids, or
                                    gases
                                </li>
                                <li>Sale items or gift cards</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-yellow-50 mt-6 p-4 rounded-lg">
                        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                            ðŸ’¡ <strong>Pro tip:</strong> If you're unsure about your
                            doctor's approval, just ask them first! It saves everyone
                            time and keeps our friendship intact. ðŸ˜Š
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white shadow-lg p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <h2 class="mb-6 font-semibold text-2xl">
                        European Union Returns
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
                        If merchandise is being shipped into the European Union,
                        you have the right to cancel or return your order within
                        14 days, for any reason and without justification. Your
                        item must be in the same condition that you received it,
                        unworn or unused, with tags, and in its original
                        packaging. You'll also need the receipt or proof of
                        purchase.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white shadow-lg p-8 rounded-2xl">
                    <h2 class="mb-6 font-semibold text-2xl">Refunds</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
                        We will notify you once we've received and inspected
                        your return, and let you know if the refund was approved
                        or not. If approved, you'll be automatically refunded on
                        your original payment method within 10 business days.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Please remember it can take some time for your bank or
                        credit card company to process and post the refund too.
                        If more than 15 business days have passed since we've
                        approved your return, please contact us at <a
                            href="mailto:info@thetismedical.com"
                            class="text-primary hover:underline"
                            >info@thetismedical.com</a
                        >.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- CTA Section -->
                <div class="bg-primary/5 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center">
                    <h3 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-xl">
                        Ready to Start Your Return?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
                        Use our simple online form to submit your return request
                        quickly and easily.
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="/returns"
                        class={buttonVariants({
                            size: "lg",
                            className: "shadow-lg",
                        })}
                    >
                        Start Return Process
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Slide>
    </main>
</Layout>
